    <p>SmartSweets is the brand that proved plant-based candy could be a mainstream success. Their gummy bears contain just 3g of sugar per bag — a 91% reduction from Haribo's 34g — using allulose and stevia as alternative sweeteners. The pectin-based formulation is gelatin-free, and the six fruit flavors are distinct and genuinely enjoyable. SmartSweets is available at Target, Whole Foods, Walmart, CVS, and Amazon, making it the most accessible premium plant-based candy brand. For the complete gummy bear comparison, read our in-depth <a href="/candy/vegan-gummy-bears/">vegan gummy bears</a> guide.</p>

