    <p>YumEarth dominates the organic plant-based candy space with a simple value proposition: USDA Organic, real fruit juice, plant-based colors, allergen-free, and a price that competes with conventional candy. At $1.29 per bag — or significantly less in bulk — YumEarth eliminates the cost barrier to switching from conventional candy. Their product line extends beyond gummy bears to include sour worms, licorice, lollipops, and hard candy, all with the same organic, vegan, allergen-free certifications. See our complete <a href="/candy/organic-gummy-bears/">organic gummy bears</a> guide for more USDA-certified options.</p>

