    <p>Surf Sweets Organic Fruity Bears have the cleanest ingredient list of any plant-based gummy candy. Real organic fruit juice is a primary ingredient, not a secondary flavoring. The top-14 allergen-free certification makes them safe for virtually any school snack policy. In our kids' taste panel (ages 5-12), Surf Sweets consistently ranked as the preferred option. The softer, fruit-snack-like texture is actually an advantage for younger children who find firmer gummies harder to chew.</p>

